        "\n",
        "> 📚 **Subject:** AI & ML ALGORITHM  \n",
        "\n",
        "> 🐍 **Language:** Python\n",
        "\n",
        "> 📖 **Description:**\n",
        "**A* (A-Star) Search Algorithm** is an **informed search algorithm** widely used for pathfinding and graph traversal problems. <br><br>\n",
        "🔍 A* combines the advantages of **Uniform Cost Search** and **Greedy Best-First Search** to efficiently find the shortest path between a start node and a goal node. <br><br> 📊 The algorithm uses an **evaluation function**: <br>\n",
        "**f(n) = g(n) + h(n)**\n",
        "<br>Where:\n",
        "> - **g(n)** = Actual cost from the start node to the current node.\n",
        "> - **h(n)** = Heuristic estimate of the cost from the current node to the goal node.\n",
        "> - **f(n)** = Estimated total cost of the solution path through node *n*.\n",
        "\n",
        "---"
      ],
